There are also some connection issues between KMS and Zookeeper. They are sporadic, that's why I'm still trying to pinpoint them, but essentially KMS can get into a perpetual connect/disconnect from Zookeeper cycle from which it eventually recovers or a restart also helps. I'm linking the relevant jira in case it is related to this issue.
